{"tid":1579780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國務院亞太助理國務卿Stilwell ：華府相信香港仍擁有足夠自治權","createTime":"2019-09-18T17:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T00:35:33.000Z","uid":101606,"like":42,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6f4f20ab2dafc0a8de463e6dbdb73bac5c4b78","tid":1579780,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:34:43.000Z","msg":"資料來源：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-dialogue-stilwell-idUSKBN1W31ZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-dialogue-stilwell-idUSKBN1W31ZM&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=3795f4e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-dialogue-stilwell-idUSKBN1W31ZM&h=2992132c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-dialogue-stilwell-idUSKBN1W31ZM</a><br />\n<br />\n重點資料：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStilwell later said Washington believed Hong Kong still retained sufficient autonomy under the terms of the 1992 U.S. Hong Kong Policy Act that allows for special economic treatment under U.S. law.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">華府相信香港仍符合1992年香港關係法中所指出既享有自治權利</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Withdrawing the extradition law is a very positive step,&quot; Stilwell told the committee.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">撤回逃犯修訂條例係港府積極的一步</span><br />\n<br />\nIn repose to another question, Stilwell said he had no information on any U.S. plan to impose sanctions on officials responsible for restricting freedoms in Hong Kong as required by a July 28 congressional resolution.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">華府對於香港官員制裁既法案暫時未有消息</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而根據番呢個post<br />\n<br />\n極重要！唔好諗住過硬，只要呢個人唔支持，《香港人權與民主法案》隨時凍過水！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579443</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nMcConnell係有機會係行政壓力下（例如trump想用黎做籌碼）hold起個bill唔discuss<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家有時間睇下國會同行政嗰邊個取態分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩漏左無講或講錯歡迎指出"},{"pid":"821ce4bf0ab5cd9a1ad84ef216752ac3b3f74f01","tid":1579780,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822290072367536480ba1221024da06c96e0d530","tid":1579780,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1120a8730d0b953963f81a96207f21e2d3fe149","tid":1579780,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e5de9b338a594abae3a07a82d927373f914059","tid":1579780,"uid":4783,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"呢條友個底好花<br />\n你起下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec5a135e8ab991eaecc13b6f83453c60442d5d1","tid":1579780,"uid":72484,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"推 雖然Solomon Yue 同 Pelosi都話兩會夠票，但都不能調以輕心呀侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6594c83ed7a83a51421db7cb4312811f76a24e","tid":1579780,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54e5de9b338a594abae3a07a82d927373f914059","tid":1579780,"uid":4783,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"呢條友個底好花<br />\n你起下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:44:55.000Z","msg":"好似唔多news講佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ba50f1